00:03:56.190 --> 00:03:57.910
I don't even know who you are.

00:03:57.910 --> 00:03:58.800
Besides,

00:03:58.800 --> 00:04:00.910
I'm just a 300-year-old fish.

00:04:01.120 --> 00:04:02.910
I know nothing about the matters

00:04:02.910 --> 00:04:04.190
from 300 years ago.

00:04:09.430 --> 00:04:10.910
I don't remember

00:04:11.420 --> 00:04:13.000
what happened 300 years ago.

00:04:14.940 --> 00:04:16.420
But your power is feeble.

00:04:17.180 --> 00:04:19.140
How could you pull out the ice spike?

00:04:23.060 --> 00:04:24.900
Before I entered the Void Land,

00:04:25.740 --> 00:04:26.820
what exactly happened?

00:04:27.260 --> 00:04:28.540
She's nothing but a traitor.

00:04:28.900 --> 00:04:30.740
Kill her now.

00:04:31.180 --> 00:04:32.020
Kill her now.

00:04:32.340 --> 00:04:33.220
Kill her now.

