00:09:03.940 --> 00:09:05.460
named Jie Chuan.

00:09:05.460 --> 00:09:07.100
The roughest of you all.

00:09:08.500 --> 00:09:09.380
This is maddening.

00:09:10.460 --> 00:09:13.100
He's a liar! A demon!

00:09:27.540 --> 00:09:30.460
Master, it's so dark.

00:10:02.460 --> 00:10:03.460
Demon... no.

00:10:03.700 --> 00:10:04.540
Demon Sovereign.

00:10:09.020 --> 00:10:09.940
